                    question: "<div style='text-align: justify;'>Rutherford’s alpha-particle scattering experiment was responsible for the discovery of<br/><br/>(a) Atomic nucleus<br/>(b) Electron<br/>(c) Proton<br/>(d) Neutron</div>",
